#: ../../source/interceptors.rst:4
msgid ""
"An interceptor is a class annotated with the ``@Injectable()`` decorator."
" Interceptors should implement the ``NestInterceptor`` interface."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/interceptors.rst:16
msgid ""
