msgid ""
"Since ``handle()`` returns an RxJS ``Observable``, we have a wide choice "
"of operators we can use to manipulate the stream. In the example above, "
"we used the ``tap()`` operator, which invokes our anonymous logging "
"function upon graceful or exceptional termination of the observable "
"stream, but doesn’t otherwise interfere with the response cycle."
